## Overview

This dashboard lists every run in the workspace with screening-level
KPIs drawn from each run's `project_scores.csv`, `vmt_screening.csv`,
and `equity_lens.csv` when present. Runs created via
`clawmodeler-engine what-if` are linked back to their baseline through
the `base_run_id` column so a planner can trace lineage across
scenarios.

No LLM is called. Every portfolio cell is read deterministically from
a run's shipped artifacts or labeled as *not yet available* when the
relevant Planner Pack module hasn't been invoked for that run.

