## Notes

- Rows without a `mean_total_score` either have no `project_scores.csv`
  or the file has no scored rows.
- The `DAC share` column is read from each run's `equity_lens.csv` —
  runs that have not invoked `planner-pack equity-lens` show `—`.
- The `Ready` column reflects the v0.7.1 QA gate (`export_ready` in
  the run's `qa_report.json`); a non-ready run has blockers listed in
  that file.

